{"id": 3132, "genre": 1001, "title": "如果办一台当代生活版春晚，你都想看些啥？", "description": "肯定不是硬拗网络流行梗就对了。（题图来自：iStock ©️Aleksei Morozov）", "record_count": 2278, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200123203505CsqdPjMfHFXlVh0y.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-23T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 352512, "content": "拒绝强行煽情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1687560}, {"id": 352519, "content": "讽刺实事性戏剧吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1687952}, {"id": 352523, "content": "想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品想看本山老师的小品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688350}, {"id": 352525, "content": "我出生以前，七八十年代，那种揭露社会现实，讽刺各种社会风气的小品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1585164}, {"id": 352270, "content": "小品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630921}, {"id": 352277, "content": "年终总结 把大事小事开心的不开心的政治经济文化来一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091824}, {"id": 352537, "content": "啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈哈哈哈哈啊哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688350}, {"id": 352538, "content": "冒个泡", "image": "img/option/option/20200605164626BU15XG6bNL2vdswK.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688350}, {"id": 352539, "content": "皮一下就很开心", "image": "img/option/option/202006051647161kFdCOnx98GQuZXU.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688350}, {"id": 352540, "content": "嘻嘻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688350}, {"id": 352541, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/202006051649152maV4nJ7xYAXqgbe.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688350}, {"id": 352286, "content": "日报用户大部分人三观很正", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680050}, {"id": 352543, "content": "没有如果，劳民伤财。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673189}, {"id": 352291, "content": "相声吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680182}, {"id": 352293, "content": "将今年重点事件以电影的形式放一边", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680203}, {"id": 352553, "content": "类似脱口秀大会吧，一场没有感动的幽默。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1689776}, {"id": 352300, "content": "国粹啊，各大戏曲整一个，好些年没看了，记得中央十一好像是戏曲的吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680114}, {"id": 352556, "content": "脱口秀，拒绝小品煽情（一切情感）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529719}, {"id": 352303, "content": "请一些实力派歌手，比如邓紫棋啊华晨宇啊等等，然后小品不要强行煽情，可以请一些年轻人来编导，吐槽一下当下催婚或者很多人对同性恋狭隘观念的现象，桥段也别那么老旧，弄一些观众意料之外的情节。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680406}, {"id": 352304, "content": "歌舞节目如果每一个都是那种合家欢大杂烩的话，就很容易令观众审美疲劳。开头是没关系如果其它歌舞节目都这样的话，就会形成一个“尿点”（这个词一般指的是电影中出现一些无聊的桥段，令观众离开座位去上厕所)其实今年春晚那段穿着旗袍跳舞进步了，既不吵吵嚷嚷，又兼顾美感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680406}, {"id": 352054, "content": "彩虹合唱团的《感觉身体被掏空》，适合社畜喜气洋洋地食用", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352055, "content": "郭德纲和于谦老师的相声，平时在家拖地就听这个", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352056, "content": "小品可以有，不要音乐一响就煽情那种，最好来点反向吐槽逼婚催生的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 489, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352057, "content": "插播的公益广告可以讲讲怎么预防传染病和吃野味恶习的危害", "image": null, "praise_count": 283, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352315, "content": "来个聊着聊着就教人一些冷知识的节目，欢乐的小品可以、唱歌也可以(希望是那种特别欢快的，不是节奏慢的、情歌之类的)，也可以年年打破传统观念，让人感受:这年春节又会有什么有趣的节目呢，期待唔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 352064, "content": "还是喜欢看小品多点…", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602226}, {"id": 352065, "content": "赵本山 沈腾 其他风格的都不爱看", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455447}, {"id": 352066, "content": "来点单口相声，聊聊生活中的趣事，比如年度沙雕集锦", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 352579, "content": "相声啊", "image": "img/option/option/20200721105914DSTa7FXrfLIOB5kM.png", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690877}, {"id": 352070, "content": "教教人们怎么找对象和摆脱负面情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560393}, {"id": 352582, "content": "相声", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1691233}, {"id": 352071, "content": "请有实力的歌手现场真唱，没有烂梗且有新意的小品，尬拒", "image": null, "praise_count": 263, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664029}, {"id": 352072, "content": "用译制腔开玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236762}, {"id": 352073, "content": "相声", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645829}, {"id": 352074, "content": "把审核员抓出来批斗。把武汉相关领导抓出来批斗", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 352076, "content": "国家的发展，人民的进步，地球的繁荣，外太空的深入，当然最重要还是家人的平安", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434374}, {"id": 352077, "content": "想看伍迪艾伦导的春晚，没有的话让李诞做个年度盘点也行", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588326}, {"id": 352078, "content": "教育教育教育！重要的事儿说三遍……", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677791}, {"id": 352592, "content": "小品吧，但是别玩煽情，一家人围着电视机看，尴尬。来点当代初高中生中考高考压力什么的和父母教育上的偏激极端（希望我妈看了能醒悟那种）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1691825}, {"id": 352343, "content": "只要不要把女性塑造成无理取闹的巨婴智障小公主，男性塑造成惧内好面子的老好人就行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643907}, {"id": 352346, "content": "我想看以前的暴走大事件", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348455}, {"id": 352603, "content": "尽量减少唱歌环节还有舞蹈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1692283}, {"id": 352610, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1692485}, {"id": 352106, "content": "太尴尬了！黄晓明调侃自己。希望以后没有了", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1642436}, {"id": 352108, "content": "聊聊游戏的危害", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151437}, {"id": 352364, "content": "脱口秀 脱口秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681792}, {"id": 352109, "content": "看央视主持人登台朗读《我的梦想》", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514198}, {"id": 352624, "content": "小品相声就使劲想办法让我们乐，不要总想着怎么让我们哭，大过年的闹心不？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693040}, {"id": 352113, "content": "谈谈年轻人的世界，聊一些热词和新文化", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315449}, {"id": 352114, "content": "拒绝过期梗，小品不要强行煽情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 175, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583466}]}